---
const { question } = Astro.props;
---

<div class="mb-5">
  <div class="text-2xl w-full font-bold">Questions & Answers</div>
</div>

<div class="mb-10">
  <QAItem question="What is your main research focus?">
    My research focuses on software and system architecture design for autonomous
    and connected systems, particularly using multi-agent based modelling and 5G/6G connectivity.
  </QAItem>

  <QAItem question="What domains do you primarily work in?">
    I work at the intersection of software engineering, autonomous driving systems,
    and next-generation wireless communication technologies.
  </QAItem>

  <QAItem question="Are you available for research collaborations?">
    Yes, I am open to national and international research collaborations in both academia and industry.
  </QAItem>
</div>

